channel.title: Help running my server?
channel.description:
My server use to run fine. But i recently had someone come out and fix my wireless internet. When he did that he messed it up somehow now my server runs but no one can connect. I want to be able to fix this soon because I already started losing players. My no-ip is working and the command prompt is open but they get the "Error connecting to server" when they try logging in. I will try to install everything again but if this persist i might need a dedicated host. If you have an idea as to what might have happen please tell me.
Edit: I forgot to mention that I had the Ethernet cord connected to my Motorola Cable Modem. And the technician connected it to from my Linksys Broadband Router to the Modem and I belive back to the Tower.
